    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ANSWER CAPSULE: Quick Reference -->
  <section style="padding: 32px 1.5rem; background: #f0f7ff; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--blue);">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7;"><strong>Angel Bail Bonds provides 24/7 bail bond services for Noble County, Oklahoma. Noble County Jail is located at 721 Cedar Street, Perry, OK 73077. Call (405) 614-3000 to begin the bail process. Our Stillwater office is just 25 miles south of Perry via I-35 — we can arrive at the jail within 30 minutes. Most inmates are released 1-4 hours after the bond is posted. We accept cash, Visa, Mastercard, Zelle, Venmo, and offer financing.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FACILITY + STEPS — combined, two-column -->
  <section style="padding: 48px 1.5rem; background: white;">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px;">

      <!-- Left: Jail Facility Details -->
      <div>
        <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">Noble County Jail Facility Details</h2>
        <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 0.9rem; border-collapse: collapse;">
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600; width: 120px;">Address</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">721 Cedar St, Perry, OK 73077</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Jail Phone</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);"><a href="tel:+15803363517" style="color: var(--blue);">(580) 336-3517</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Inmate Info</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);"><a href="tel:+15803361001" style="color: var(--blue);">(580) 336-1001</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Capacity</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">48 inmates</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Avg. Bookings</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">~4,233/year (~8/day)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Sheriff</td>
